[1] Yemen
Date: Wed 20 Jun 2018
Source: WHO [edited]
https://reliefweb.int/sites/reliefweb.int/files/resources/100618_suspectedcases_who_color.pdf


Yemen: cholera suspected cases
------------------------------
The map at this URL lists the total number of suspected cholera cases through 10 Jun 2018 to be 1 107 144.

--
